Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] According to the press bureau of the Russian border 
guards, on Wednesday three armed men were detained crossing the 
Tajik-Afghan border from Afghanistan at the Khorog border unit. 
During the operation Russian border guards came under gun fire 
from three points in the Afghan territory. They retaliated. 
One of the gunmen was wounded. None of the border guards was 
hurt. 

